To create tiny websites having pretty urls

Version 2.0 (2.feb.2015)
-Examples were deleted
-Added the use of composer
-Now it can load static pages that stary in pages folder which is also configurable
-Added errors folder to manage all errors in loading method,classes ans views
-Config constants were fixed

Version 1.1 (15.Mar.2012)
-Now you can use NotORM library by changing the app/config/config.php USE_DB to TRUE
-Support of loading views into a variable
-added a app/config/config.php file

Version 1.0 (09.Mar.2012)
-loading controllers and methods
-passing vars into views
